<HL>
   Mathematicians Race to Develop
   New Kinds of Trading Instruments
   ----
   By Craig Torres
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
10/18/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C1
